alse,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Wider tires ultimately deliver improved traction, fuel efficiency, and productivity. But there are some key things to keep in mind:","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8176-b101-f22060623840","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-8147-875e-fa9a08aabdce"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:09:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:09:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"bulleted_list_item","bulleted_list_item":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Farmers and growers that change to a wider tire should ensure that the equipment has the recommended wheel widths to support the tire size.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Farmers and growers that change to a wider tire should ensure that the equipment has the recommended wheel widths to support the tire size.","href":null}],"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81c8-866e-dfd42b90fbdc","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-8147-875e-fa9a08aabdce"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:09:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:09:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"bulleted_list_item","bulleted_list_item":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Tire manufacturers typically offer a recommended wheel width with acceptable alternative wheels or rim widths.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Tire manufacturers typically offer a recommended wheel width with acceptable alternative wheels or rim widths.","href":null}],"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81e0-b3af-edf7ed54aa0e","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-8147-875e-fa9a08aabdce"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:09:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:09:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Ultimately, a tire is a compromise between size, materials, and air working together to deliver the best possible performance. For any farmer or grower, selecting the right wheel and tire combination will maximize equipment performance by optimizing load carrying capability and delivering the power to plow, plant, harvest, or spray his crops.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Ultimately, a tire is a compromise between size, materials, and air working together to deliver the best possible performance. For any farmer or grower, selecting the right wheel and tire combination will maximize equipment performance by optimizing load carrying capability and delivering the power to plow, plant, harvest, or spray his crops.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-819b-951c-eb98af605e23","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-8147-875e-fa9a08aabdce"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:09:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:09:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragra